# quickjs.patch - Patches to QuickJS core engine
#
# Target files: quickjs/quickjs.c, quickjs/quickjs.h
# Applied by: make quickjs-deps (copies quickjs/ to bin/<platform>/quickjs/ then patches)
#
# Features added:
#
#   1. JS_GetClosureVars(ctx, func) - API to inspect closure variables
#      Used by qn:introspect for function serialization.
#      Returns JS object { varName: value, ... } for the closure.
#
#   2. Import error source locations
#      Import resolution errors now include the importing file and line number.
#      Example: "Could not find export 'foo' in module 'bar.js' (imported at main.js:5)"
#      - Adds line_num field to JSImportEntry struct
#      - Captures line number during import statement parsing
#      - Enhanced error messages in js_link_module()
#
